short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This chrome extension convert comment sections in GitHub as CLI

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Include "ghc-auto-completion.txt" in the root of any repository, then the extension reads it and makes CLI based on the content of it. Each commands should be separated with a line break in the txt file.
